        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-8 ">
                    <h1>What is DYRCT?</h1>
                    <p>
			DYRCT is a destination and location management platform making address sharing, navigation and trip management simple, fast and accurate.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        From sharing a single location with an individual or group to sharing multi-location folders to your entire contact list, Dyrct is effective, easy to use and will simplify your life.
                    </p>
		<div ng-show="readmoreflag">
<p>Dyrct is a Mobile and Web supported network of user-managed online Connected Identities (CiD) which are easily created, saved and shared among users. Privacy and viewing restrictions can be altered for your entire contact list or customised for individual contacts.
</p>
<p>This CiD forms the basis of common-destination user groups and multi-CiD themed folders both of which have wide social networking, travel and business applications.
</p>
<p>Our ‘one-touch’ navigation launch interface avoids the complexity & input inaccuracy typical of traditional navigation devices.
</p>
<p>Go Dyrct and let your destination find you.
</p>
</div>
